OL,3,C2025 could be the UK's hottest year on
OL,4,Crecord, forecasters say
OL,6,FThe UK could be on course for its
OL,7,Fwarmest year on record, forecasters
OL,8,Fsay, as climate change pushes
OL,9,Ftemperatures to new highs.
OL,11,FThe Met Office said 2025 is on track
OL,12,Fto be among the warmest years recorded
OL,13,Fand could overtake 2022 to become the
OL,14,Fhottest.
OL,16,FSo far, the average annual temperature
OL,17,Fis tracking at 10.05C, ahead of the
OL,18,Fprevious record of 10.03C set in 2022.
