OL,6,FA forecasted cold spell over Christmas
OL,7,Fmeans the final figure is not yet
OL,8,Fconfirmed.
OL,10,FIf confirmed, 2025 will be only the
OL,11,Fsecond year in observational records
OL,12,Fwhere the UK's annual mean temperature
OL,13,Fhas topped 10C.
OL,15,FFour of the last five years will then
OL,16,Fappear in the top five warmest years
OL,17,Fsince records began in 1884, with all
OL,18,Fof the top 10 warmest years occurring
OL,19,Fin the last two decades.
