OL,3,C2025 could be the UK's hottest year on
OL,4,Crecord, forecasters say
OL,6,FA new record has been previously set
OL,7,Ffor the UK annual mean temperature
OL,8,Ffive times this century ` in 2002,
OL,9,F2003, 2006, 2014 and 2022.
OL,11,FMike Kendon, a senior scientist at the
OL,12,FMet Office, said: "At this stage it
OL,13,Flooks more likely than not that 2025
OL,14,Fwill be confirmed as the warmest year
OL,15,Fon record for the UK."
