OL,3,C2025 could be the UK's hottest year on
OL,4,Crecord, forecasters say
OL,6,FHe added: "In terms of our climate, we
OL,7,Fare living in extraordinary times. The
OL,8,Fchanges we are seeing are
OL,9,Funprecedented in observational records
OL,10,Fback to the 19th century."
OL,12,FProfessor of climate science
OL,13,FFriederike Otto said: "The finding is
OL,14,Fdevastating and utterly unsurprising,
OL,15,F10C might not sound very warm, but it
OL,16,Fis an average and means much higher
OL,17,Ftemperatures in the summer, high
OL,18,Ftemperatures that would have never
OL,19,Fbeen possible are now common and that
OL,20,Fis not good news."
