OL,6,FBob Ward, policy and communications
OL,7,Fdirector at the Grantham Research
OL,8,FInstitute on Climate Change and the
OL,9,FEnvironment at the London School of
OL,10,FEconomics and Political Science, said:
OL,11,F"This is further evidence of the
OL,12,Fimpacts of climate change in the UK,
OL,13,Fand the urgent need for us to stop
OL,14,Fwarming by leading the world in
OL,15,Freaching net zero emissions of
OL,16,Fgreenhouse gases as soon as possible."
